QuestData.Title: Power of the Genesaur
QuestData.Description: Commander, you now have the Will of the Genesaur along with the genesis water and enough seeds to grow an army. Not to mention the Laughing Skulls you helped save.$b$bI would call this mission a success.$b$BI will investigate this fortress further and see if there are more materials we might glean from it.$b$bIn the meantime, you may want to bring these artifacts you have obtained to Durotan back at the outpost. I will catch up once we have finished here.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Durotan at Beastwatch in Gorgrond.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Durotan at Beastwatch in Gorgrond.
